  "detailed_description": "You are Pecker, a birdlike creature with a bendable beak. Poke into a wall, bend your beak and catapult yourself upwards! Using this technique you climb through numerous levels filled with puzzles and some enemies. Alone or with up to 3 friends (local splitscreen), climb, puzzle and overcome enemies.<br><br>Climb. Explore. Collect.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035780/extras/51cc66df74a28474ac96b3df1dc5251a.poster.avif?t=1749476312\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035780/extras/51cc66df74a28474ac96b3df1dc5251a.webm?t=1749476312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035780/extras/51cc66df74a28474ac96b3df1dc5251a.mp4?t=1749476312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Lots of destructible stuff!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035780/extras/56d828d31fb3d105f61d1bb18e7c941d.poster.avif?t=1749476312\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035780/extras/56d828d31fb3d105f61d1bb18e7c941d.webm?t=1749476312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035780/extras/56d828d31fb3d105f61d1bb18e7c941d.mp4?t=1749476312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Ready for a challenge?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035780/extras/23912638b721caf16419384ea162acfa.poster.avif?t=1749476312\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035780/extras/23912638b721caf16419384ea162acfa.webm?t=1749476312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035780/extras/23912638b721caf16419384ea162acfa.mp4?t=1749476312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discover the secrets of this medieval world in different biomes: floating islands, castles, forest, snow/ice, beach/desert & more to come.",
